@UPSHelp
Fuck you UPS. As I write this, the 3rd dumbass supervisor that I've talked to today, simply put my call on hold because she didn't want to deal with me. This is bullshit and COMPLETELY UNACCEPTABLE. I've been waiting for this package to be delivered since Friday! WTF!!!

@LenchoSS I can understand your frustration as you have been waiting for your package. Let my team review the tracking history with you to see if we may be of assistance. DM us the tracking number, name, and complete address on the package. ^TT https://t.co/wKJHDXWGRQ
